  <brief_title>Safety and Efficacy Study of Bimosiamose Cream to Treat Psoriasis</brief_title>
  <official_title>Multi-center, Randomized, Double-blind, Placebo-controlled Phase 2 Study to Evaluate the Safety and Efficacy of Bimosiamose 5% Cream for the Treatment of Patients With Chronic Plaque Type Psoriasis</official_title>
  <sponsors>
